   <li>Creed, C., Beale, R., Dower, P., 2014, &quot;Digital tools for physically impaired visual artists&quot;, <i>Proceedings of the 16th international ACM SIGACCESS conference on Computers &amp; accessibility</i>, pp.&nbsp;253--254</li>
