   <li>Beale, R., 2006, &quot;Improving Internet Interaction: From theory to practice&quot;, <i>Journal of the American Society for Information Science and Technology. Perspectives on Search User Interfaces: Best Practices and Future Visions</i> <b>57</b>, pp.&nbsp;829--833 &ndash;
