   <li>Beale, R., 2004, <a href="http://www.bcs-hci.org.uk/interfaces/interfaces60.pdf">&quot;Ferraris and Fiestas&quot;</a>, <i>Interfaces</i> <b>Autumn</b>, pp.&nbsp;5</li>
   <li>Beale, R., 2004, <a href="http://www.bcs-hci.org.uk/interfaces/interfaces59.pdf">&quot;Internet ubiquity or social inequality?&quot;</a>, <i>Interfaces</i> <b>Summer</b>, pp.&nbsp;5</li>
